Name: ENDGAME: Survival
About the game: Big group of people will be dropped into a desert island where they will have to survive. There are no rules, but there are advantages for the ones that will fight and kill, every kill, a Contestant will be rewarded with Points that can be used to buy advantages like better guns and even vehicles The only way to get rescued is by buying a rescue with credits. - Explore a vast island - Hunt animals for food - Defeat enemies and take their loot - Use guns and traps to protect your base - Gather natural resources such as special minerals and wood to build survival tools and structures - Build a base and tools to survive
